Detailed Description

cvmx_tra::_trig0_cmd

TRA_TRIG0_CMD = Trace Buffer Filter Command Mask

Description:

Notes: Note that the trace buffer does not do proper IOBDMA address compares. Thus, if IOBDMA is set, then the address compare must be disabled (i.e. TRA_TRIG0_ADR_MSK set to zero) to guarantee that IOBDMAs are recognized as triggers.
